	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Here are some Ideas that I was toying with:<br />
<br />
To balance the priest classes, the clerics could be given some additional and more powerfull utilities along the line of our spell haste. <br />
<br />
- give us a buff that increases the  Spell Effectiveness as some Bard songs do. (make it analog to the Blessing line of spells)<br />
<br />
- add a set of AA (or disc not sure yet) that increase the spell effectivness, healing output, spell haste and mana regen. Make them to be for the whole group. Only one can be used at a time and with a set duration and a reasonable reuse time (2 to 5 mins). (btw I would love to see the proposed AA affect our ch and the Druid one also, this could be very usefull on raids and help the druids take their places in rots, while making the clerics usefull in raidsituations). This is kind of like the prayer idea mentioned elsewhere, but I would like to be able to cast while using this ability.<br />
<br />
This way we would bring some utility to groups that would add dps or increase healing output.<br />
