	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I pulled for years as a Cleric.  Somewhere in the archives of this forum you might be able to find my post on why clerics are one of the Top-3 pullers in the game.   I do not think that is the case any longer because the mobs move to fast and hit too hard.   The simple fact is that the puller will die sometimes, and that is a hard situation for groups to deal with in today's environment.<br />
<br />
The items you suggested are fairly meager improvements to the class.   Others already have those roles and those roles are their reason for being in the group, we dont want to go that route.  Give us nukes just below druids, give us super fast self heals and better defense so we become the healer that can take the beating.  Give us some basic utility, invisibility, some group resists, and such.</font></p>
	
